Spec: OpenPGP Type Shim
Purpose:
  Provide local TypeScript declarations for the OpenPGP API surface used by this project.

Structure:
  openpgp.d.ts: OpenPGP declaration shim.

Owns:
  openpgp.d.ts

Must:
  Declare only OpenPGP types and functions used by project code or tests.

Exposes:
  OpenPGP module declarations
